title: $\beta$-O$_{2}$ Structure
comments:
Data for $\beta$-O$_{2}$ was taken at 30K. 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/A_hR2_166_c-001}{$\alpha$-As ($A7$)}, \href{current_web_home_dir/A_hR2_166_c-002}{rhombohedral graphite}, and \href{current_web_home_dir/A_hR2_166_c-003}{$\beta$-O} have the same AFLOW prototype label, A\_hR2\_166\_c. They are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt --params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files. Hexagonal settings of rhombohedral structures can be obtained with the option {\tt --hex}.
